

---blochlib/examples/mpiplay/

	-- get_put.cc --> simple demonstration of the 'get' and 'put' MPI commands
		          using the MPI controller
	
	-- datatype.cc --> test the get and passing of the oodles of data types
	                   in blochlib
	
	-- reduce.cc --> tests the 'reduce' functions for a simple MPI sum
	
	-- reconstruct.cc --> tests the reconstruct functions in the MPI container
